        </div>
        <h3 class="regular mt1">Sharing</h3>
        <p>Noodles recipes are private, but you share a public link, embed one on the web, or even download a PDF.</p>
        <p><a href="http://www.getnoodl.es/s/2rAW0DA" class="btn bg-blue">Check out a recipe</a></p>
      </section>
      <section class="left-align bs-bb">
        <div class="circle bg-orange shadow inline-block mx-auto" style="line-height: .9">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="m1 fill-white"><path d="M8.1 13.34l2.83-2.83L3.91 3.5c-1.56 1.56-1.56 4.09 0 5.66l4.19 4.18zm6.78-1.81c1.53.71 3.68.21 5.27-1.38 1.91-1.91 2.28-4.65.81-6.12-1.46-1.46-4.2-1.1-6.12.81-1.59 1.59-2.09 3.74-1.38 5.27L3.7 19.87l1.41 1.41L12 14.41l6.88 6.88 1.41-1.41L13.41 13l1.47-1.47z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="regular mt1">Cook Mode</h3>
        <p>Easily follow a recipe while you're cooking &mdash; check off ingredients, add notes, save photos, and more.</p>
        <p><a href="http://www.getnoodl.es/recipes/45/cook" class="btn bg-blue">Try Cook Mode</a></p>
      </section>
    </article>
    <article class="px3 md-col-8 mx-auto mt3 md-flex flex-between">
      <section class="left-align bs-bb md-col-6 mr3">
        <div class="circle bg-orange shadow inline-block mx-auto" style="line-height: .9">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="m1 fill-white"><path d="M3 13h8V3H3v10zm0 8h8v-6H3v6zm10 0h8V11h-8v10zm0-18v6h8V3h-8z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="regular mt1">Collections</h3>
        <p>Organize recipes into collections, or send a public link to the collection so friends can use the recipes.</p>
        <p><a href="http://www.getnoodl.es/c/2A1J3Q" class="btn bg-blue">See a collection</a></p>
      </section>
      <section class="left-align bs-bb md-col-6">
        <div class="circle bg-orange shadow inline-block mx-auto" style="line-height: .9">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="m1 fill-white"><path d="M3.9 12c0-1.71 1.39-3.1 3.1-3.1h4V7H7c-2.76 0-5 2.24-5 5s2.24 5 5 5h4v-1.9H7c-1.71 0-3.1-1.39-3.1-3.1zM8 13h8v-2H8v2zm9-6h-4v1.9h4c1.71 0 3.1 1.39 3.1 3.1s-1.39 3.1-3.1 3.1h-4V17h4c2.76 0 5-2.24 5-5s-2.24-5-5-5z"/></svg>
