      </section>
    </article>
    <section class="mx-auto px3 md-col-6">
      <blockquote class="h3 mx-auto mt2">
        &ldquo;Whether you want to keep your own recipes or you need to jot a recipe you find online or on TV, Noodles is handy.&rdquo;
